  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2cbaeec8dbe84e069925173ac3a6210b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dlg_Ruins_GM_Opening
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ElementalAlchemist.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _speaker: Grand Master
  _lines:
  - The Ruins. Where the first alchemists reached too far, and the world broke beneath their hands. This is the realm of Soul.
  - Breath gave you life. Flesh gave you form. Here you face the last and hardest truth of all, what a thing is worth once it can never die.
  - The Guardian of the Ruins keeps the final Fragment. Find it, answer what it asks, and the Fragment of Soul will be yours.
  - I will be waiting when it is done. Go.
